Opus Consulting Solution


Reflexis
Reflexis provides a full specturm of Retail Execution Solutions that on a high level includes the real time store management, task operation and workforce management solutions. For customers, reflexis can provide an individual product on demand or can provide of suite of products that help customers to unleash the potential of their business. Reflexis provide solution on the cloud and on mobile devices.
Reflexis has customers in various verticals (industries) like departmental stores (burlington, coop city), soft goods(Levis, american exoress outfitters), hard goods (Bose, gowireless), Wellness and fitness (24 hour fitness, weight watchers).
Reflexis also has good partnership with top notch companies like services partner cognizant one out of many, IBM and microsoft as solution partner out of many other. 
